The following packages are required by Shoes for Sugar, but are not provided on the XO-1 default install:

libjpeg-devel rubygems rubygem-rake gtk2-devel ruby-devel pango-devel cairo-devel giflib-devel

You can use yum to install all of these dependencies.

To enable Sugar-specific functionality in the Shoes toolkit, Set the SUGAR environment variable before running rake.
